<ul local-id=3D"6687dfc2-7f7c-4cde-9559-aedc41dc8c45">
<li local-id=3D"30e310b5-3480-4db0-bc74-381ac0c7bf36">
<p local-id=3D"12d6e524-39ce-4aaa-864e-716e1422d3f6"><strong>INRODUCTION</s=
trong></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f13023fa-fe38-482a-a4e0-b53d8eed1582">This document details =
the <strong>end-to-end Private Brand (PB) Opportunity Workflow</strong> wit=
hin the Salesforce system, covering all associated business processes, auto=
mation, integrations, and custom logic components. The document serves both=
 as a functional overview and a technical blueprint of how Private Brand op=
portunities are created, managed, and approved for <strong>Distributors, Re=
tailers, Sites, and Influencers</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"7a3659cd-6929-435e-84e2-3b66e3334751">It also include relate=
d flows such as:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"2c692588-f715-457c-b308-c38af8b33a61">
<li local-id=3D"003872a6-7dd4-4786-8941-20cd88ce04bb">
<p local-id=3D"30af978e-b1ac-492d-8629-2bd96fdbe978">Cross-Pod Order Creati=
on (e.g., PB Opportunity for a Manufacturing Customer)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0492cfae-eaaa-4033-9f02-958024849074">
<p local-id=3D"09c45e43-d914-42b1-b24b-c47f1f1a5177">Project Order Lifecycl=
e</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"585a2af3-9743-417e-8ecb-4991a2cb3f0d">
<p local-id=3D"77911dcb-54f0-4c12-94c5-33518823b8d2">Credit Pricing Workflo=
ws</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f144d9e6-01fe-49a4-b2f2-edaa8befb537">
<p local-id=3D"80165b0e-923e-412a-b39f-f74dc663a3eb">Multi-layered Approval=
 Mechanisms (Freight, Address Change, Price Breach, etc.)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"c94311cb-81f1-4500-a699-b1e4d166a6c9"></p>
<p local-id=3D"29998ce8-8bd9-43d8-bfc0-8d6b93871238"><strong>High- Level Wo=
rkflow Diagram</strong></p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper =
image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"conflue=
nce-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20250707-024701.png" width=3D=
"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"984ba3fb54f958fe8dfeef900bb284311dadba6a14383=
78dc0e85643582ab294" data-image-src=3D"https://jswone.atlassian.net/wiki/do=
wnload/attachments/2553085956/image-20250707-024701.png?version=3D1&amp;mod=
ificationDate=3D1751856424406&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-heigh=
t=3D"335" data-width=3D"1193" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-link=
ed-resource-id=3D"2571403268" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linke=
d-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-=
20250707-024701.png" data-base-url=3D"https://jswone.atlassian.net/wiki" da=
ta-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-containe=
r-id=3D"2553085956" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"8" data-media=
-id=3D"b4dc3275-d750-476a-8187-7857fca96e11" data-media-type=3D"file" heigh=
t=3D"131"></span>
<p local-id=3D"a2dd4ff5-4be9-49f5-9558-02f7c31cc69b"></p>
<p local-id=3D"f432dbab-f7f0-4f83-97fe-4783a69def8d"><strong>Workflow Steps=
 :</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"0c679879-032d-4669-b63e-eb252f6ea10f"><strong>Account Creati=
on:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"d59af103-a817-49ad-80f5-5017212770c7">
<li local-id=3D"23c9666c-01b3-464d-b861-77ed966d701b">
<p local-id=3D"aff891fd-7ea3-48ca-b26d-9af4e1b88473">There is an integratio=
n with the Customer Portal (CCP). Once an account is signed up in the porta=
l, CCP pushes the data to Salesforce, where we create a registered account =
in Salesforce.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d4575280-306b-4725-a30a-b324427ef664">
<p local-id=3D"2cbd4099-fa19-4857-823c-3d785a5752cd">If an unregistered acc=
ount already exists in Salesforce with the same email, GSTIN, or phone numb=
er, the account is updated to a registered account.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"839fe708-20b0-4c88-b40b-ba73f3bc464c"><strong>Components</st=
rong>:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"22=
2c17ac-99a7-46c2-97f8-81df7f3753d8" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 168.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 589.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"937aefa4-c088-417d-8e01-8bfe75d34e20">
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"97dacbae-3197-49c3-a=
a19-ec6379b96872" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"6d20a318-3e8c-4f75-b380-946092d7c32e">&nbsp;</p></th>
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"2a225811-f68b-4cf4-b=
c1f-d7f2cc7faff0" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"57402b28-1af1-4348-bc0e-729f333fda2a"><strong>Components</st=
rong></p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"25e56d1d-be74-4f24-8afe-65c397550b9c">
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#ffffff" data-local-id=3D"21039208-b6b7-4abf-a=
