<p local-id=3D"99856db1-e91e-42db-857d-db2f1f2bec3c"></p>
<p local-id=3D"c71ad0aa-7632-4c17-bb44-578fb6cf8c20"><strong><span class=3D=
"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"9198e9cb-d43a-425b-b8bb-c90d9543ab1a">O=
pportunity creation:</span></strong></p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-=
file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img cla=
ss=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20250707-025353.=
png" width=3D"336" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"999595615885a310795ae6aa583942f0=
153e7fd2a8d6317d256f2bb4fd839792" data-image-src=3D"https://jswone.atlassia=
n.net/wiki/download/attachments/2553085956/image-20250707-025353.png?versio=
n=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1751856834470&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv=
2" data-height=3D"653" data-width=3D"336" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"=
0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"2571534340" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1=
" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-ali=
as=3D"image-20250707-025353.png" data-base-url=3D"https://jswone.atlassian.=
net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resou=
rce-container-id=3D"2553085956" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"8=
" data-media-id=3D"4697ffaa-754d-4fc8-b610-cc8b6236551c" data-media-type=3D=
"file" height=3D"651"></span>
<p local-id=3D"b9d2677c-aa70-460b-bb45-a436023a9232"></p>
<p local-id=3D"4429dfa7-89f0-4ce7-b5b4-ccec0ee2505b">The process initiates =
from an existing Account record in Salesforce. A new Private Brand Opportun=
ity is created by clicking the <strong>JSW One for TMT</strong> action butt=
on on the Account page. This triggers a Lightning Web Component (LWC) that =
guides the user through a series of interactive screens. Users can add or r=
emove SKUs, fetch pricing dynamically, and proceed to submission. If the en=
tered selling price differs from the fetched price, the system automaticall=
y invokes the appropriate approval process.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"e7=
3c5c9d-90cc-4fe2-903c-b6306435ca53" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 168.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 589.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b2c427c0-fe2d-4172-aa91-62a1f7f82701">
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"8f380faa-d773-4e5c-8=
648-7cc252f8457e" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"acb95f0b-772e-4f9d-99f5-59caf6071ed0">&nbsp;</p></th>
<th data-highlight-colour=3D"#f0f1f2" data-local-id=3D"caf83f18-b965-46b4-b=
5ea-3e72d4416212" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"712abf79-39df-4d05-8408-8ab384348980"><strong>Components</st=
rong></p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"2aa7c531-a691-4653-be92-d51feebec024">
<td data-local-id=3D"c4e70840-2ac2-43e0-bea6-3ed0ab00616f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"32ab0961-8fc6-4f85-b2bb-bcbc095ac096">Class Name</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"0c2b209b-861e-4449-9252-2dea6cbc1226" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"412f7b86-5359-4f1d-b36d-10082a4f3b53">JSW_PricingEngineAPI ,=
createOrderRetailerClass ,PricingRequestWrapper, PB_PricingAPIResponseWrapp=
er</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"923b07d9-218b-4b8e-83ee-94e02953cb92">
