<p local-id=3D"f379b2bc-7d7b-4199-8f57-da97e36fb5bc">Similarly, if an Oppor=
tunity has already been created and the user wishes to modify it, they can =
click the <strong>Edit Opportunity</strong> action button. This triggers an=
 LWC that follows a process similar to Opportunity creation, allowing users=
 to add, update, or delete SKUs as needed.</p>
