<p local-id=3D"83972ff1-376a-4fc4-9e1e-5456952f6fc2"><strong>Project Opport=
unity creation: </strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"bbb72f50-1026-4ad2-abda-40d117aaeb83"></p><span class=3D"con=
fluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manu=
al-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image=
-20250728-163650.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"5e235798f384549=
3cdc36dc1b7d18471951761935dbd430f0059b68095fc4313" data-image-src=3D"https:=
//jswone.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/2553085956/image-20250728-=
163650.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1753720611918&amp;cacheVersio=
n=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"492" data-width=3D"577" data-unresolved-=
comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"2641395858" data-linked-reso=
urce-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-res=
ource-default-alias=3D"image-20250728-163650.png" data-base-url=3D"https://=
jswone.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" =
data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"2553085956" data-linked-resource-conta=
iner-version=3D"8" data-media-id=3D"9704a815-0f16-4d40-ab00-9508cd9274dc" d=
ata-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"399"></span>
<p local-id=3D"f6502932-d08b-4a33-a339-c5529d5343a5">The process begins fro=
m an existing Account record in Salesforce. A new Project Opportunity is cr=
eated by clicking the <strong>JSW One for TMT</strong> button. This launche=
s a Lightning Web Component (LWC) that guides the user through a step-by-st=
ep flow: selecting order type as Project, choosing ship-to address type, de=
livery address, and then selecting TMT type and diameter from available SKU=
s. Users can specify the required quantity, and the opportunity is submitte=
d along with associated line items.</p>
<p local-id=3D"198b1833-2229-4db0-931b-80c13ee211f8"></p>
