<p local-id=3D"e5eaa59f-70d5-4ea4-8730-ebb85743ed8e">Similarly, if an Oppor=
tunity has already been created and the user wishes to modify it, they can =
click the <strong>Edit Opportunity</strong> action button. This triggers an=
 LWC that follows a process similar to Opportunity creation, allowing users=
 to add, update, or delete SKUs as needed.</p>
<p local-id=3D"f270f41e-eebf-4a78-aba4-95120c97bd71"><strong>Note:</strong>=
 Pricing details will not be retrieved through the Pricing API in this proc=
ess.</p>
<p local-id=3D"68013446-dab2-4167-88fd-7d4f049acc8d">This process is also a=
pplicable to all accounts except Retailer and Distributor (this contains Se=
lf and Retailer project type).</p>
