<p local-id=3D"988000a4-1914-4cdb-8a59-0e87c4916ce4"></p>
<ul local-id=3D"4023a7ac-1bf6-45f0-a9ed-5dd80242f5e1">
<li local-id=3D"801a93c3-669b-4fec-a9e6-7aa6b2027e3a">
<p local-id=3D"2e771782-5085-46d7-ba66-c040770c18b5"><strong>Private Brands=
 - include phantom SKU logic</strong><br>
Ticket reference - <span class=3D"confluence-jim-macro jira-issue" data-jir=
a-key=3D"SF-4206"> <a href=3D"https://jswone.atlassian.net/browse/SF-4206?s=
rc=3Dconfmacro" class=3D"jira-issue-key">SF-4206</a> </span></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"e5751bfa-3620-4cf0-86f4-321aa8f92b62">In the Edit Opportunit=
y workflow of the PB, the 12mm phantom SKU was not getting auto-deleted aft=
er creation. This logic has now been enhanced in the LWC JavaScript and the=
 <code>editOrderRetailerController</code>, which deletes the 12mm dummy rec=
ord and updates the comment as =E2=80=98Phantom=E2=80=99. The 12mm SKU with=
 the =E2=80=98phantom=E2=80=99 comment is created only to fetch data from t=
he price engine.</p>
